WEBVTT

00:10:30.480 --> 00:10:32.576
It is your inner voice.

00:10:32.600 --> 00:10:34.416
So let's recapitulate.

00:10:34.440 --> 00:10:36.496
We have the mask, the outward voice,

00:10:36.520 --> 00:10:39.616
the inside of the mask, your inward voice,

00:10:39.640 --> 00:10:41.656
and then you have your inner voice.

00:10:41.680 --> 00:10:43.736
And I like to see this one
as the puppeteer

00:10:43.760 --> 00:10:46.200
that holds the strings
of the whole system.

00:10:47.440 --> 00:10:49.056
Your inner voice is

00:10:49.080 --> 00:10:51.920
the one you hear
when you read a text silently,

00:10:53.320 --> 00:10:55.560
when you rehearse
for an important conversation.

00:10:56.760 --> 00:10:58.376
Sometimes is hard to turn it off,

00:10:58.400 --> 00:11:02.456
it's really hard to look at the text
written in your native language,